  • public class UserBlogQuery
extends BlogQuery<BlogData,BlogQueryParameters>
    QueryDefinition to retrieve BlogListItems with details about access rights for a given user. If the query instance does not define a user ID the ID of the current user will be taken.

    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
